# The act of despairing or becoming desperate; a giving up of hope.
# A state of despair, or utter hopeless; abandonment of hope; extreme recklessness; reckless fury.
# Act of showing extreme amount of anxiety to achieve or obtain something otherwise one's situation would be hopeless. Once you show your desperation to someone, the other person would take advantage of your anxiety.

